    12                                  ; PROBLEM:
    13                                  ; Read the input.txt file in 5-byte chunks.
    14                                  ; The file is in the same directory as the asm file.
    15                                  ; For each chunk, print its 1-based index and its contents.
    16                                  ; Remember to free unused resources.
    17                                  ;
    18                                  ; EXAMPLE:
    19                                  ; Input file:
    20                                  ; ABCDEfghijKLMNO
    21                                  ;
    22                                  ; Resulting output:
    23                                  ; Chunk 1: ABCDE
    24                                  ; Chunk 2: fghij
    25                                  ; Chunk 3: KLMNO
    26                                  ;
    27                                  ; DOCUMENTATION:
    28                                  ; - x86 instructions: https://mrlini.github.io/instr/
    29                                  ; - C functions: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/c-runtime-library/reference/crt-alphabetical-function-reference?view=msvc-160#s
